name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Big Als Golf Group Booking System

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Big Als Golf Group Booking System

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The purpose of this extension is to facilitate the booking of tee times for golf clubs and groups that use Golf Genius and Fore-Tees to manage their competitive rounds.  This version is specifically designed for use by Big Als golf group.
